snippet.title: Star Trek: Infinite | Your First Day
snippet.description:
Star Trek: Infinite is available October 12 for PC and Mac, pre-purchase now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1622900/Star_Trek_Infinite/

Taking on the mantle of a leader for an entire people can be a daunting prospect. That is why we have prepared a short onboarding to arm you with the knowledge to approach this new position with confidence. It will not be an easy task but we trust in your ability to adapt to the situation!
